425
00:38:49,720 --> 00:38:50,840
Lakukan sesuai yang dia katakan dulu.

426
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:58,150
Hati-hati.

427
00:38:59,030 --> 00:39:00,720
Jangan menyirami kelopak bunga dan daun.

428
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:02,510
Baik.

429
